  "texts": [
    "Premise 5 of my argument is as follows: P5: If misaligned AI which is capable of permanently disempowering humanity and tries to permanently disempower humanity will be built by 2100, then humanity will be permanently disempowered by 2100.",
    "This premise is very close to a tautology.",
    "I defined 'being capable of X' as meaning 'If one tries X, then X'.",
    "Thus, tautologically, if misaligned AI is capable of permanently disempowering humanity and tries to disempower humanity, then humanity will be disempowered.",
    "The only qualification which saves P5 from being a mere tautology is the reference to time."
  ],
